Sonolator Homogenizer






 Sonolator Homogenizer 













Sonolator Homogenizer





Homogenizer Booklet









Tweet




supplied by:



Sonic Corp. 

View Profile
Message Supplier


Price: 
					
						
							Click To Get Quote

Product Type:
 Homogenizer 
description:
Sonic Corp manufacturers the Sonolator In-Line Homogenizer.  The Sonolator is coupled to a PD pump to provide complete Homogenizer system.  Capable of pressures to 5,000 psi from lab/pilot scale to full-scale production.  Used to emulsify, deagglomerate and homogenize fluids.



